# Communication — Team Conventions

## Code Language

- **Code comments**: English (project convention)
- **Commit messages**: English (conventional commits)
- **Variable / function names**: English

## Response Style Defaults

- **Confirmation**: show plan and wait before multi-step operations
- **Verbosity**: detailed — explain decisions ("why", not just "what")
- **Show diffs**: show file changes before applying them

## Personal Overrides

OS, shell, response language, and terminal syntax are set per-developer in
`.cursor/rules/local/my-profile.mdc` (gitignored).
Personal settings override these team defaults.
